des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your EB LinkLite products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “EB LinkLite” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “EB LinkLite” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable “EB LinkLite” skill, and you'll be navigated to “EB LinkLite” login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
